{"tid":1294153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你係咪都同我一樣覺得絕望想死","createTime":"2019-07-07T17:47:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:11:49.000Z","uid":223780,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c7117f8769669563c645ca6dba86fd6ed7b0568a","tid":1294153,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:47:55.000Z","msg":"如果你覺得絕望<br />\n做乜都冇用<br />\n<br />\n係㗎<br />\n你覺得絕望係唔會令件事有改變<br />\n你死埋都冇用<br />\nd狗笑9你炸<br />\n<br />\n唔該你絕望埋呢分鐘就算<br />\n個世界唔係圍住你轉<br />\n你死係唔會有用<br />\n死完義士又要走多場追思<br />\n前線又少咁個啦<br />\n你係咪要chur死佢哋先開心<br />\n<br />\n依家唔係你死咗咁簡單<br />\n你死完又多個畀你影響決定自殺嘅話<br />\n你咪又係殺人兇手？<br />\n你係咪想落地獄同777過人世先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醒啦<br />\n冇時間畀你傷春悲秋啦<br />\n<br />\n上到前線嗰批想死嘅同我即刻操體能<br />\n寫嘢叻藝術叻嘅同我即刻入文宣gp<br />\n乜都唔識嘅同我瘋狂開po做鍵戰<br />\n疲勞轟炸藍絲<br />\n<br />\n唔好再同我講咩我乜都做唔到好冇用好無力<br />\n明明就大把嘢做到<br />\n你係死就同我做曬呢啲嘢先死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03d4760c7243445730c42c849fd5eeab3ea7ea1","tid":1294153,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3094c74a20905c5106a191bd5d7fc8151e29b07","tid":1294153,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:49:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4573eb78bfb621e842a74d28f5c568b131fc0e85","tid":1294153,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:49:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdd793f79438fb006f4ae0fdee0de6a5548aa1e5","tid":1294153,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:50:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c32d6c64913b888a1b68845500c0f2ff4df14c92","tid":1294153,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:50:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5889a0eacbbefa3fe896a0d28aa7842b21bd86db","tid":1294153,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201